<BaseLayout title="About" description="A bit about Colin McCloskey.">
  <div class="page-wrap">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Colin McCloskey — a software engineer based in the US. I've spent
      most of my career building things on the web and thinking about how
      software teams work (and don't).
    </p>

    <p>
      I care a lot about craft: readable code, honest communication, and tools
      that don't make you feel bad about yourself. I'm skeptical of complexity
      by default and try to write software that a future version of me will
      actually want to maintain.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of work I read too much, cook a reasonable amount, and have
      opinions about coffee that I try not to share unless asked.
    </p>

    <h2>Find me elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/mccolin">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/mccolin">LinkedIn</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
